text: Vedrana Vučićević (born 14 March 1985) is a Bosnia and Herzegovina cross- country skier. She competed in the women's 10 kilometre classical at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Bosnia and Herzegovina Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Sarajevo
